data.description: Welcome to an elegant 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that seamlessly blends modern comfort with outdoor allure. This residence welcomes you with high ceilings, creating an open and spacious ambiance that sets the stage for comfortable living.Notably, this home features a new roof. An essential upgrade that ensures both structural integrity and peace of mind for years to come. Step outside, and you'll discover a screened-in lanai that leads to a sparkling pool, ideal for refreshing swims and outdoor relaxation. Adjacent to the pool, a covered sitting area invites you to unwind in the shade, savoring the serene views of your backyard oasis.The heart of the home lies in the kitchen, which includes a charming breakfast nook. Here, you can enjoy your morning coffee while basking in the natural light that pours in through the windows. This residence boasts new pool equipment, enhancing the functionality and efficiency of your pool. Additionally, one of the bathrooms has been remodeled, adding a touch of modern luxury to your daily routine.This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. With its high ceilings, new roof, screened-in lanai with pool, covered sitting area, breakfast nook, and bathroom remodel, it offers not only comfort but also style and functionality. It's a place where you can relax, entertain, and enjoy the comforts of everyday living in a welcoming and beautifully updated environment.
